<A>__{halfway down, pi hits water. he dives, searching for his family. the hall lights flicker the passage falls dark an instant before the emergency lights come on in the water below, which nearly reaches the ceiling. pi dives, trying to swim against the flowing current; he's astonished to find a zebra swimming toward him, passing overhead. he tries to swim further, but the enormous force of rushing water and air is too great; he scrambles backward, groping toward the stairwell.}
